OL,4,CColdplay: Band ready for backlash over 
OL,5,Ceco-friendly world tour                
OL,6, Coldplay's next tour will partly be    
OL,7, powered by a dancefloor that generates 
OL,8, electricity when fans jump up and down,
OL,9, and pedal power at the venues.         
OL,11,FIt's part of a 12-point plan to cut    
OL,12,Ftheir carbon footprint, two years after
OL,13,Fthe band pledged not to tour until they
OL,14,Fcould do so in a more sustainable way. 
OL,16,FSinger Chris Martin told the BBC in his
OL,17,Ffirst interview about the plans that   
OL,18,Ffans will be on "kinetic flooring".    
OL,20,F"When they move, they power the        
OL,21,Fconcert," he said.                     
